<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hóa đơn thanh toán</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #1a1a1a;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0 0 24px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .divider {
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .info-section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .info-label {
            color: #666;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .info-value {
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .movie-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .invoice-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .invoice-table th {
            background-color: #f0fdf4;
            color: #108f27;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .invoice-table td {
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .text-center {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .text-right {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .text-left {
            text-align: left;
        }

        .footer-note {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 24px 0 0 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer-note p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-style: italic;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .signature {
            margin: 32px 0 0 0;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .signature p {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 4px 0;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .signature .team {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a1a1a;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Xác Nhận Đặt Vé Thành Công</h1>

        <hr class="divider">

        <div class="info-section">
            <div class="movie-name">{{movie_name}}</div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">Phòng chiếu: </span>
                <span class="info-value">{{cinema_room}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">Suất chiếu: </span>
                <span class="info-value">{{show_time}} - {{show_date}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">Mã vé: </span>
                <span class="info-value">{{booking_code}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">Ngày đặt: </span>
                <span class="info-value">{{booking_date}}</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <table class="invoice-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th style="width: 40px;">STT</th>
                    <th>Mặt hàng</th>
                    <th style="width: 60px;">SL</th>
                    <th style="width: 90px;">Đơn giá</th>
                    <th style="width: 90px;">Thành tiền</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {{{invoice_items_rows}}}
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <div class="footer-note">
            <p>Vui lòng đưa mã này cho nhân viên tại quầy vé để nhận vé.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="signature">
            <p>Trân trọng,</p>
            <p class="team">Hệ thống quản lý rạp chiếu phim SE100.Q11</p>
            <p class="contact">Email: <a href="mailto:nhom10.se100q11@gmail.com">nhom10.se100q11@gmail.com</a></p>
            <p class="contact">Hotline: +84 936458120</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>